PART 3: H/p GROWTH PATTERN
======================================================================

  H/p for Interval tournament:
  p= 5: H/p = 3
  p= 7: H/p = 25
  p=11: H/p = 8457
  p=13: H/p = 285475

  Factorizations of H/p:
  p= 5: H/p = 3 = 3
  p= 7: H/p = 25 = 5 × 5
  p=11: H/p = 8457 = 3 × 2819
  p=13: H/p = 285475 = 5 × 5 × 19 × 601

  H/p modular analysis:
  p=5: H/p=3, mod 5=3, mod 4=3, mod 2=1
  p=7: H/p=25, mod 7=4, mod 6=1, mod 3=1
  p=11: H/p=8457, mod 11=9, mod 10=7, mod 5=2
  p=13: H/p=285475, mod 13=8, mod 12=7, mod 6=1

